jasperReport.name: BPK9_24_40
jasperReport.queryString: SELECT * FROM ( SELECT acccredit.visit_date "Date", acccredit.visit_time "Time", acccredit.financial_discharge_date "DischargeDate", acccredit.financial_discharge_time "DischargeTime", acccredit.hn "HN", acccredit.vn "VN", acccredit.patient_name "Patient", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='01' THEN acccredit.linecost ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ต้นทุนยา", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='02' THEN acccredit.linecost ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ต้นทุนเวชภัณฑ์", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id<>'01' AND acccredit.account_id<>'02' THEN acccredit.linecost ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ต้นทุนอื่นๆ", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='01' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่ายา", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='02' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่าเวชภัณฑ์", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='03' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "Lab", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='04' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "Xray", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='05' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ทันตกรรม", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='06' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "กายภาพ", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='07' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ล้างไต", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='08' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่าอุปกรณ์", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='09' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่าแพทย์", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='10' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่าบริการพยาบาล", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='11' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่าบริการโรงพยาบาล", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='12' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่าห้อง", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='13' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "ค่าอาหาร", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='14' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "เหมาจ่าย", SUM(CASE WHEN acccredit.account_id='15' THEN acccredit.linesale ELSE 0 END)::FLOAT "อื่นๆ", SUM(acccredit.linesale)::FLOAT "รวมค่าบริการORDERED", COALESCE(accdebit."รวมค่าบริการBILLED", 0) "รวมค่าบริการBILLED", accdebit.all_plan "สิทธิการรักษาทั้งหมด" FROM bpk_account_credit_detail acccredit LEFT JOIN ( SELECT receive_date, visit_id, all_plan, SUM(linesale)::FLOAT "รวมค่าบริการBILLED" FROM bpk_account_debit_detail WHERE receive_date='$P!{dBeginDate}' GROUP BY receive_date, visit_id, all_plan ) accdebit ON acccredit.visit_id=accdebit.visit_id AND accdebit.receive_date='$P!{dBeginDate}' WHERE acccredit.verify_date='$P!{dBeginDate}' AND acccredit.fix_visit_type_id='0' GROUP BY acccredit.visit_date, acccredit.visit_time, acccredit.financial_discharge_date, acccredit.financial_discharge_time, acccredit.hn, acccredit.vn, acccredit.patient_name, "รวมค่าบริการBILLED", accdebit.all_plan ORDER BY acccredit.visit_date, acccredit.visit_time ) tmp WHERE tmp."รวมค่าบริการORDERED"=tmp."รวมค่าบริการBILLED" ORDER BY tmp."Date", tmp."Time"
